---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Lint term consistency in project docs

Usage: mf term lint [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --fix                
      --root <PATH>        
      --config <PATH>      
      --dry-run            
      --project <PROJECT>  
  -v, --verbose...         
      --format <FORMAT>    [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
  -q, --quiet              
      --no-color           
  -h, --help               Print help
  -V, --version            Print version
